                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great book if you already know Software Product Lines, but..</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
